WEBVTT

00:02:58.668 --> 00:03:00.041
Morali bi se toplo obleči,

00:03:00.041 --> 00:03:01.371
da bi telesno tempreaturo

00:03:01.371 --> 00:03:03.590
ohranili nad 35 stopinj Celzija,

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:06.460
sicer bi začeli močno drhteti,

00:03:06.460 --> 00:03:08.169
postali bi zmedeni

00:03:08.169 --> 00:03:09.663
in nato bi padli z neba, saj bi

00:03:09.663 --> 00:03:10.799
zaradi podhladitve

00:03:10.799 --> 00:03:13.179
izgubili nadzor nad mišicami!

00:03:14.272 --> 00:03:16.221
Zakon idealnega plina pravi,

00:03:16.221 --> 00:03:17.927
da s padanjem tlaka

00:03:17.927 --> 00:03:19.756
narašča prostornina plina.

00:03:19.756 --> 00:03:21.756
Če bi prehitro odleteli navzgor,

00:03:21.756 --> 00:03:24.620
bi se inertni plin v telesu
hitro razširil

00:03:24.620 --> 00:03:27.457
kot gazirana pijača, ko jo pretresemo.

00:03:27.457 --> 00:03:30.032
Ta pojav se imenuje